          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2021-10-22T16:59:18Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text>
            <![CDATA[ <p>This bill makes the state law of Utah applicable to the use of motor vehicles (including off-highway vehicles) on the portions of each of Burr Trail Road, Cathedral Road, Hartnet Road, Highway 24, Notom Bullfrog Road, Polk Creek Road, Oil Ranch Road, and Baker Ranch Road that are located within the boundaries of the Capitol Reef National Park in Utah. </p>]]>
          </text>
          <updateDate>2021-04-29T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
